.PP
Call a method already defined in the state.
\f[V]KeyPath\f[R] is a list of keys to the method.
\f[V]KeyPath\f[R], \f[V]Method\f[R], \f[V]Args\f[R] and \f[V]Result\f[R]
are automatically encoded/decoded.
